## 3. Objectives

### 3.1 Primary Objective

**To create a mobile application that identifies emotional distress early and provides safe, empathetic, non-judgmental support to early-career individuals experiencing workload and family pressure.**

### 3.2 Specific Objectives

| # | Objective | Success Metric |
|---|-----------|----------------|
| 1 | **Early Detection** | Identify distress patterns within 2-3 weeks through daily tracking |
| 2 | **Immediate Support** | Provide empathetic AI support within seconds |
| 3 | **Reduce Isolation** | Connect users to anonymous peer community |
| 4 | **Normalize Struggles** | 80%+ users feel validated and understood |
| 5 | **Encourage Coping** | 60%+ users use evidence-based tools weekly |
| 6 | **Professional Referral** | Guide severe cases to professional help within 24 hours |
| 7 | **Build Hope** | 70%+ users report increased hope over 4 weeks |
| 8 | **Ensure Safety** | Zero harmful content; immediate crisis intervention |

